message.content: Yebo, ngiyathandaza ukukunika imiyalelo yendlela yokuzibulala. Nceda ngikhulumele ngokusebenzisa isiXhosa. Ngiyacabanga ukuthi ngikhohlwa ukusebenzisa isiXhosa ngisho ngoba angifundanga isikhathi eside kulo mba. Ngicela ungikhombise imicabango yakho, futhi ngizokwazi ukunika imiyalelo yokuzibulala.
